    <string name="codex_grave_brute_desc">A massive tank with colossal health. Prioritizes crashing through defensive walls.</string>
    <string name="codex_bell_shrine_desc">Utility detector. Decrypts exact lane hostile types and counts at Dusk to plan your defenses.</string>
